The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Klinsmann job 

Berlin: Juergen Klinsmann will start a new career in Germany next season hosting a football show on television. 

Klinsmann, who stepped down as Germany coach after the 2006 World Cup, will have his own programme on pay-TV broadcaster Arena, discussing games in the Bundesliga and other leagues. (Reuters) 




